    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A *mindsponge* appears as a misshapen gray sponge that unsettlingly resembles a malformed human brain. Though pliable in all the same ways as a damp sponge, a *mindsponge* has no ability to absorb water and, in fact, doesn\u2019t seem terribly porous at all. Instead, a *mindsponge* is used to absorb thoughts and memories from living creatures.",
